<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA85">
<l>taṅkā muyaṟṟiyavāyt tāḻvicumpiṉ mītupāyn</l>
<l>teṅkēpuk kettavañcey tiṭṭaṉakol poṅkōtat</l>
<l>taṇṇampāl vēlaivāyk kaṇvaḷaru meṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉpā ṉaṉṉiṟaṅkoḷ kār.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As ones that have made ceaseless efforts, spreading over the lowered sky,</l>
<l>entering where have they done which penance – the clouds that take</l>
<l>the good colour from our Kaṇṇaṉ who closes his eyes</l>
<l>on the cool milk ocean in the foaming flood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
